<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - KIET Group of Institutions</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .about-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .about-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }
        .about-img {
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                    <!-- Carousel -->
                    <div id="campusCarousel" class="carousel slide mb-3" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <img src="https://www.kiet.edu/assets/images/kiet-campus.jpg" class="d-block w-100 about-img" alt="KIET Campus">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://www.kiet.edu/assets/images/kiet-library.jpg" class="d-block w-100 about-img" alt="KIET Library">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://www.kiet.edu/assets/images/kiet-lab.jpg" class="d-block w-100 about-img" alt="KIET Lab">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#campusCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#campusCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2 class="about-title mb-3">About KIET Group of Institutions</h2>
                    <p>
                        Established in 1998, <strong>KIET Group of Institutions</strong> is a premier educational institution located in Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh. The institute is renowned for its commitment to academic excellence, innovation, and holistic development of students.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        KIET offers a wide range of undergraduate and postgraduate programs in Engineering, Management, Pharmacy, and other disciplines. With state-of-the-art infrastructure, experienced faculty, and a vibrant campus life, KIET empowers students to become industry-ready professionals and responsible citizens.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Accredited by NAAC with Grade 'A+' and NBA</li>
                        <li>Strong industry collaborations and placement record</li>
                        <li>Focus on research, innovation, and entrepreneurship</li>
                        <li>Active student clubs and extracurricular activities</li>
                    </ul>
                    <!-- Collapsible Vision & Mission -->
                    <p>
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#visionMission" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="visionMission">
                            View Vision & Mission
                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="visionMission">
                        <div class="card card-body mb-3">
                            <strong>Vision:</strong> To be a center of excellence in technical and professional education, research, and innovation.<br>
                            <strong>Mission:</strong> To impart quality education, foster research and innovation, and nurture responsible professionals for the betterment of society.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Modal Trigger -->
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#moreInfoModal">
                        More About KIET
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="moreInfoModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="moreInfoModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="moreInfoModalLabel">More About KIET</h5>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            KIET Group of Institutions is known for its vibrant campus life, excellent placement opportunities, and a strong alumni network. The institute regularly organizes workshops, seminars, and cultural events to ensure the holistic development of students.
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap JS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>